1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:24,750 --> 00:01:28,930
[The Fearless Season 1]

3
00:01:29,300 --> 00:01:31,810
[Episode 40]

4
00:01:32,030 --> 00:01:34,229
They have no reason to trick me, do they?

5
00:01:37,030 --> 00:01:38,550
Okay.Then there's no need to rush.

6
00:01:38,550 --> 00:01:40,479
We'll talk when the money arrives.

7
00:01:42,750 --> 00:01:43,280
Alright.

8
00:01:43,390 --> 00:01:45,720
I have something urgent to do. I have to go.

9
00:01:48,030 --> 00:01:48,830
Who is it?

10
00:01:52,410 --> 00:01:52,770
Mom.

11
00:01:52,789 --> 00:01:54,160
You're really back!

12
00:01:54,190 --> 00:01:54,670
Wait!

13
00:01:54,950 --> 00:01:55,390
Mom!

14
00:01:55,470 --> 00:01:57,670
You tricked Liu Ming into going to America,

15
00:01:57,670 --> 00:01:58,990
while you came back.

16
00:01:58,990 --> 00:02:00,470
You left him there alone.

17
00:02:00,700 --> 00:02:02,670
You even transferred all the money from the company.

18
00:02:02,670 --> 00:02:03,510
I... I can explain it!

19
00:02:03,510 --> 00:02:04,830
Do you think you can walk all over us?

20
00:02:04,830 --> 00:02:05,110
You...

21
00:02:05,110 --> 00:02:06,120
Please hear me out!

22
00:02:06,120 --> 00:02:07,920
I'm his mother. I'm not dead yet!

23
00:02:08,150 --> 00:02:09,229
I'm right here to defend him!

24
00:02:09,229 --> 00:02:11,039
I came back to prepare myself for pregnancy!

25
00:02:11,039 --> 00:02:11,970
Let me explain.

26
00:02:11,990 --> 00:02:12,590
What?

27
00:02:12,590 --> 00:02:14,080
I came back to prepare myself for pregnancy.

28
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:15,080
Just hear me out.

29
00:02:15,110 --> 00:02:15,550
Fine.

30
00:02:16,270 --> 00:02:18,350
Today, if you can't give me a satisfactory explanation,

31
00:02:18,350 --> 00:02:19,110
I'll call the police

32
00:02:19,110 --> 00:02:20,150
and have them arrest you right away!

33
00:02:20,150 --> 00:02:21,110
Don't do that!

34
00:02:21,780 --> 00:02:23,530
I can explain everything.

35
00:02:25,270 --> 00:02:25,880
Now say it.

36
00:02:26,590 --> 00:02:29,110
I came back here after reaching a consensus with Liu Ming.

37
00:02:29,110 --> 00:02:29,590
In fact,

38
00:02:30,060 --> 00:02:31,710
I've always wanted to visit you in Lingnan,

39
00:02:31,710 --> 00:02:33,930
but something in Jingbei keeps me occupied.

40
00:02:33,930 --> 00:02:37,390
I'm back because I wanna prepare myself for pregnancy. It's true.

41
00:02:37,390 --> 00:02:38,110
Mom.

42
00:02:38,280 --> 00:02:40,230
Do you think I'm evil or what?

43
00:02:40,390 --> 00:02:41,829
When Liu Ming and I arrived in America,

44
00:02:41,829 --> 00:02:43,960
we couldn't adapt to the new environment.

45
00:02:43,960 --> 00:02:46,230
At that time, I just got pregnant.

46
00:02:46,270 --> 00:02:48,329
I even threw up after drinking water.

47
00:02:48,930 --> 00:02:51,410
Because of that, I had a miscarriage.

48
00:02:52,230 --> 00:02:54,690
Thereafter, I couldn't get pregnant again.

49
00:02:55,390 --> 00:02:56,600
I went to the doctor.

50
00:02:56,790 --> 00:02:58,550
The doctor said I was too weak

51
00:02:58,570 --> 00:03:00,110
and that I needed rest and nutrition.

52
00:03:00,110 --> 00:03:02,370
But I couldn't get used to the food there.

53
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:04,240
As you know,

54
00:03:04,270 --> 00:03:05,550
Liu Ming couldn't even take care of himself.

55
00:03:05,550 --> 00:03:07,610
How was he supposed to take care of me?

56
00:03:07,930 --> 00:03:09,150
We ran out all the options.

57
00:03:09,150 --> 00:03:10,410
In order to have a baby,

58
00:03:10,870 --> 00:03:12,590
I had to come back and stay a while.

59
00:03:12,590 --> 00:03:14,690
I knew Ming would be worried, so I told him

60
00:03:14,690 --> 00:03:16,480
I came back only to visit my family.

61
00:03:16,480 --> 00:03:18,010
I didn't tell him the truth.

62
00:03:18,430 --> 00:03:19,680
Mom, trust me.

63
00:03:19,700 --> 00:03:21,290
You've misunderstood me.

64
00:03:22,990 --> 00:03:25,190
At this point, you're still lying to me.

65
00:03:25,990 --> 00:03:27,550
How is your preparation for pregnancy

66
00:03:27,550 --> 00:03:29,829
relevant to the money of the company?

67
00:03:31,590 --> 00:03:32,550
Mom.

68
00:03:32,790 --> 00:03:34,430
As you know, Luo Yingzi is trying

69
00:03:34,430 --> 00:03:35,829
to figure out where that money has gone.

70
00:03:35,829 --> 00:03:37,170
However, when Liu Ming left, he made her

71
00:03:37,170 --> 00:03:39,520
the corporate representative of Grand Property.

72
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:41,290
That has given her the right to investigate

73
00:03:41,290 --> 00:03:43,690
where the money is on behalf of the company.

74
00:03:43,840 --> 00:03:44,390
Also,

75
00:03:44,870 --> 00:03:46,270
she called the police, didn't she?

76
00:03:46,270 --> 00:03:49,800
She claimed that Liu Ming defrauded the bank and illegally seized property.

77
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:51,340
That's why I didn't dare to keep the money

78
00:03:51,340 --> 00:03:53,200
in Ming Xin's corporate account.

79
00:03:53,610 --> 00:03:56,530
The police easily found out that the money

80
00:03:56,670 --> 00:03:59,930
had once been transferred from Grand Property to Ming Xin.

81
00:04:00,270 --> 00:04:01,110
Mom,

82
00:04:01,540 --> 00:04:03,110
it's true that I have transferred the money,

83
00:04:03,110 --> 00:04:04,510
but I haven't used any of it,

84
00:04:04,510 --> 00:04:06,570
as it is now safely kept in my account.

85
00:04:07,110 --> 00:04:08,970
Let's say what you told me is true.

86
00:04:08,970 --> 00:04:11,900
Luo Yingzi has traced the money from Grand Property to Ming Xin.

87
00:04:11,900 --> 00:04:14,030
She's likely to trace it to you, right?

88
00:04:14,660 --> 00:04:16,790
The company belongs to the three of us.

89
00:04:16,910 --> 00:04:18,970
Liu Ming and I take the biggest share.

90
00:04:19,180 --> 00:04:20,269
Without any notice,

91
00:04:20,269 --> 00:04:22,150
you secretly transferred the money away.

92
00:04:22,150 --> 00:04:23,480
What do you mean by that?

93
00:04:24,910 --> 00:04:26,370
Listen, this is a warning.

94
00:04:26,790 --> 00:04:27,850
Within three days,

95
00:04:28,600 --> 00:04:31,710
you must transfer 21 million to our account.

96
00:04:31,990 --> 00:04:33,310
Don't you dare to keep a penny for yourself!

97
00:04:33,310 --> 00:04:34,030
Otherwise,

98
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:35,960
I'll make you suffer!

99
00:04:37,150 --> 00:04:39,610
Mom, what's the rush for?

100
00:04:39,970 --> 00:04:42,230
Luo Yingzi keeps a close watch on the money.

101
00:04:42,230 --> 00:04:43,710
Can we deal with it when things cool off?

102
00:04:43,710 --> 00:04:44,360
No.

103
00:04:45,200 --> 00:04:46,040
I don't trust

104
00:04:46,270 --> 00:04:47,470
anyone.

105
00:04:47,700 --> 00:04:50,560
I won't feel secured unless the money is in my hands.

106
00:04:50,580 --> 00:04:52,010
Just transfer it back in three days.

107
00:04:52,010 --> 00:04:54,130
If you don't, I'll call the police.

108
00:04:55,780 --> 00:04:57,330
Can you give me a few more days?

109
00:04:57,330 --> 00:04:58,909
I can't handle such a huge sum of money in just three days.

110
00:04:58,909 --> 00:05:01,110
Three days. That's all the time you have.

111
00:05:01,110 --> 00:05:02,170
If you don't agree,

112
00:05:02,790 --> 00:05:04,720
we'll take it to the police office.

113
00:05:06,790 --> 00:05:08,150
Fine. I agree.

114
00:05:09,270 --> 00:05:10,960
Mom, please don't be mad.

115
00:05:12,470 --> 00:05:14,800
You came from afar. Where are you staying?

116
00:05:15,110 --> 00:05:17,030
Why don't you stay at my place?

117
00:05:17,030 --> 00:05:18,230
I have a vacant room here.

118
00:05:18,230 --> 00:05:19,690
I won't stay at your place.

119
00:05:20,390 --> 00:05:23,620
You might murder me at night for money.

120
00:05:24,770 --> 00:05:25,470
I'm leaving.

121
00:05:25,470 --> 00:05:27,470
I'll see what happens in three days.

122
00:05:28,030 --> 00:05:28,710
Listen.

123
00:05:29,030 --> 00:05:30,890
You'd better not pull any stunts.

124
00:05:31,270 --> 00:05:33,470
If three days later, I can't find you here,

125
00:05:33,470 --> 00:05:35,800
I'll immediately go to the police office!

126
00:05:35,830 --> 00:05:36,960
You have my promise.

127
00:05:39,550 --> 00:05:40,480
Mom, let me get that for you.

128
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:41,280
Don't bother.

129
00:05:43,430 --> 00:05:44,420
Mom, take care.

130
00:05:58,500 --> 00:06:00,100
Hello, Qiwei. Where are you?

131
00:06:00,270 --> 00:06:01,350
I want to see you.

132
00:06:02,140 --> 00:06:02,540
Okay.

133
00:06:02,710 --> 00:06:04,840
I'll wait at the place we usually go to.

134
00:06:05,570 --> 00:06:08,490
The police easily found out that the money

135
00:06:08,670 --> 00:06:11,220
had once been transferred from Grand Property to Ming Xin.

136
00:06:11,220 --> 00:06:12,020
No problem.

137
00:06:12,550 --> 00:06:15,110
You may go back to Lingnan now.

138
00:06:15,630 --> 00:06:17,770
I'm supposed to meet her in three days.

139
00:06:18,550 --> 00:06:20,910
I don't think you will see her at that time.

140
00:06:21,110 --> 00:06:22,840
Just go. I'll keep you updated.

141
00:06:23,110 --> 00:06:26,030
I'll leave the rest to you, Yingzi.

142
00:06:26,470 --> 00:06:28,330
I know you are good at everything.

143
00:06:28,470 --> 00:06:29,030
Let's go.

144
00:06:29,230 --> 00:06:29,930
Yingzi.

145
00:06:31,030 --> 00:06:31,980
Look,

146
00:06:32,490 --> 00:06:35,120
I've done everything you asked me to.

147
00:06:35,150 --> 00:06:36,750
I've been very cooperative.

148
00:06:37,110 --> 00:06:39,110
Will you withdraw your allegations

149
00:06:39,180 --> 00:06:40,180
against Liu Ming?

150
00:06:40,200 --> 00:06:41,860
The police have opened a case.

151
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:45,180
If they don't think he has committed crimes,

152
00:06:45,590 --> 00:06:47,120
they will dismiss the case.

153
00:06:47,290 --> 00:06:49,850
However, if they think the opposite,

154
00:06:50,470 --> 00:06:52,590
they'll institute a public prosecution.

155
00:06:52,590 --> 00:06:53,050
Then...

156
00:06:53,400 --> 00:06:54,530
Should that happen,

157
00:06:54,710 --> 00:06:56,590
I may write him a letter of understanding.

158
00:06:56,590 --> 00:06:57,050
Well...

159
00:06:57,470 --> 00:06:57,909
-Bye.
-But...

160
00:06:57,909 --> 00:06:58,670
Luo Yingzi,

161
00:06:58,790 --> 00:07:00,990
don't you think you're being too cruel?

162
00:07:03,060 --> 00:07:04,320
Not as cruel as you are.

163
00:07:08,150 --> 00:07:09,590
Only three days to go.

164
00:07:10,710 --> 00:07:13,110
She knows what Liu Ming's mom is capable of.

165
00:07:13,230 --> 00:07:14,470
If this time she can't run away,

166
00:07:14,470 --> 00:07:16,400
she will never get a second chance.

167
00:07:17,030 --> 00:07:17,790
But before she flees away,

168
00:07:17,790 --> 00:07:20,150
she'll definitely ask Ding Qiwei for money.

169
00:07:20,150 --> 00:07:21,350
She has suffered a big loss.

170
00:07:21,350 --> 00:07:23,750
There's no way she'd leave without a fight.

171
00:07:23,880 --> 00:07:25,460
Liu Ming's mom has met with her.

172
00:07:25,460 --> 00:07:28,110
So Liu Ming and his mom's account isn't useful to her anymore.

173
00:07:28,110 --> 00:07:30,670
When she makes the transfer, maybe...

174
00:07:31,030 --> 00:07:33,470
We can talk to Mr. Ding and Mr. Liang.

175
00:07:33,710 --> 00:07:35,470
We'll say it's a business-to-business transfer

176
00:07:35,470 --> 00:07:37,710
which doesn't accept a third-party account.

177
00:07:37,710 --> 00:07:38,460
It's a way to force Wen Li

178
00:07:38,460 --> 00:07:40,320
to expose her corporate account.

179
00:07:40,710 --> 00:07:42,180
This time, we'll find the account

180
00:07:42,180 --> 00:07:44,270
that we've been looking for, right?

181
00:07:44,500 --> 00:07:45,450
Yes, I guess.

182
00:07:46,270 --> 00:07:48,350
Have more confidence in yourselves.

183
00:07:50,150 --> 00:07:52,240
Wen Li is a slippery liar.

184
00:07:52,350 --> 00:07:53,960
I can't guarantee that we'll be able

185
00:07:53,960 --> 00:07:55,830
to bring her corporate account to light.

186
00:07:55,830 --> 00:07:56,790
Don't worry.

187
00:07:56,909 --> 00:07:59,040
Even if we can't find that account out,

188
00:07:59,590 --> 00:08:01,910
we'll nail her with Ms. Xiao's case.

189
00:08:01,910 --> 00:08:04,170
There's no way she can get away with this.

190
00:08:04,750 --> 00:08:07,550
I admire how fierce Mr. Chen is.

191
00:08:09,200 --> 00:08:10,350
I will hunt down

192
00:08:10,350 --> 00:08:12,030
anyone who messes with you.

193
00:08:18,470 --> 00:08:19,930
Okay. We should get going.

194
00:08:20,520 --> 00:08:23,270
Don't. Aren't we supposed to talk about strategies?

195
00:08:23,270 --> 00:08:24,350
You are invincible.

196
00:08:24,350 --> 00:08:25,580
What do you need us for?

197
00:08:25,580 --> 00:08:26,590
I'll let you take care of everything.

198
00:08:26,590 --> 00:08:27,230
Bye.

199
00:08:31,280 --> 00:08:32,580
To pursue a girl like Yingzi,

200
00:08:32,580 --> 00:08:34,159
you need a proper strategy.

201
00:08:39,340 --> 00:08:39,940
Mr. Ding,

202
00:08:40,360 --> 00:08:42,360
I think Mr. Chen's proposal is good.

203
00:08:43,110 --> 00:08:44,310
I agree to play along.

204
00:08:51,310 --> 00:08:52,240
Hello, Mr. Ding.

205
00:08:54,990 --> 00:08:56,830
I have learned

206
00:08:56,960 --> 00:08:58,990
how much you value wealth.

207
00:08:59,120 --> 00:09:00,120
I assure you

208
00:09:00,230 --> 00:09:01,470
that the lost money

209
00:09:01,510 --> 00:09:02,840
will be returned to you.

210
00:09:04,050 --> 00:09:05,710
Today I came to Mr. Liang's office

211
00:09:05,710 --> 00:09:07,430
to ask for his help with my plan

212
00:09:07,710 --> 00:09:09,380
to find out the corporate account

213
00:09:09,380 --> 00:09:11,180
registered to Wen Li's name.

214
00:09:11,590 --> 00:09:13,190
Rest assured, alright?

215
00:09:14,020 --> 00:09:14,700
That's it.

216
00:09:15,070 --> 00:09:15,510
Bye.

217
00:09:16,870 --> 00:09:17,470
All done.

218
00:09:19,750 --> 00:09:20,430
Mr. Liang,

219
00:09:21,430 --> 00:09:22,630
I was about to tell you to come.

220
00:09:22,630 --> 00:09:24,090
Meet this gentleman here.

221
00:09:24,380 --> 00:09:25,710
He is Mr. Chen, a lawyer.

222
00:09:25,780 --> 00:09:26,180
Hello.

223
00:09:26,320 --> 00:09:27,250
Hello, Mr. Ding.

224
00:09:31,300 --> 00:09:31,900
Mr. Liang,

225
00:09:31,930 --> 00:09:33,990
Wen Li and I will go on a business trip to America.

226
00:09:33,990 --> 00:09:35,770
The two million I've received from you

227
00:09:35,770 --> 00:09:36,900
might not be enough.

228
00:09:37,350 --> 00:09:39,510
I was wondering if you could

229
00:09:39,510 --> 00:09:41,380
give me that 30 million in one transfer.

230
00:09:41,380 --> 00:09:42,600
Mr. Ding, Mr. Liang,

231
00:09:42,630 --> 00:09:44,830
since you're having a private conversation,

232
00:09:44,830 --> 00:09:46,490
maybe I should excuse myself.

233
00:09:51,930 --> 00:09:53,730
What's your trip to America for?

234
00:10:11,600 --> 00:10:12,350
What's up?

235
00:10:13,040 --> 00:10:13,640
He agreed.

236
00:10:14,930 --> 00:10:15,800
On what?

237
00:10:15,830 --> 00:10:17,110
The 28 million.

238
00:10:19,310 --> 00:10:20,780
Did your dad agree to give it to us?

239
00:10:20,780 --> 00:10:23,070
I tried so hard to persuade him.

240
00:10:24,710 --> 00:10:25,990
Why are you packing?

241
00:10:28,410 --> 00:10:29,760
I thought you weren't coming.

242
00:10:29,760 --> 00:10:31,220
I thought I'd leave alone.

243
00:10:32,350 --> 00:10:34,700
I didn't do a good job and I let you down.

244
00:10:35,110 --> 00:10:35,720
But now,

245
00:10:35,780 --> 00:10:37,940
all the problems have been solved.

246
00:10:38,390 --> 00:10:39,720
Come on. Let me tell you.

247
00:10:42,390 --> 00:10:44,710
My dad entrusted Mr. Liang with 30 million.

248
00:10:44,710 --> 00:10:45,830
We've got 2 million of it.

249
00:10:45,830 --> 00:10:47,190
As for the remaining 28 million,

250
00:10:47,190 --> 00:10:47,870
Mr. Liang said he could

251
00:10:47,870 --> 00:10:49,600
transfer it to us anytime.

252
00:10:50,310 --> 00:10:51,990
Do you have a corporate account?

253
00:10:51,990 --> 00:10:52,850
You need to tell me one.

254
00:10:52,850 --> 00:10:56,310
Mr. Liang said it should be a business-to-business transfer.

255
00:10:58,750 --> 00:10:59,430
Qiwei,

256
00:11:00,520 --> 00:11:03,460
I want the money to be transferred to an American account.

257
00:11:03,460 --> 00:11:05,220
I've been working with

258
00:11:05,240 --> 00:11:06,350
a reliable third party.

259
00:11:06,350 --> 00:11:08,230
Maybe we should use their account.

260
00:11:08,230 --> 00:11:10,230
But Mr. Liang particularly reminded me

261
00:11:10,230 --> 00:11:13,300
that the money must be transferred to a corporate account registered to your name.

262
00:11:13,300 --> 00:11:16,300
He said since it's a business-to-business transfer,

263
00:11:16,480 --> 00:11:18,710
if the receiving end wasn't an account of yours,

264
00:11:18,710 --> 00:11:22,910
the finance department in my company might not be able to send the money out.

265
00:11:23,110 --> 00:11:23,710
Honey,

266
00:11:23,940 --> 00:11:26,150
don't you own a company in America?

267
00:11:26,220 --> 00:11:27,110
We'll have the money transferred to...

268
00:11:27,110 --> 00:11:28,190
I sure do.

269
00:11:28,400 --> 00:11:30,260
I'll tell you about it right away.

270
00:11:30,370 --> 00:11:32,370
Ask them to transfer the money soon.

271
00:11:33,310 --> 00:11:34,070
Sure.

272
00:11:34,400 --> 00:11:35,200
Listen.

273
00:11:35,230 --> 00:11:36,190
When we get to Hollywood,

274
00:11:36,190 --> 00:11:37,190
we'll shoot our first movie.

275
00:11:37,190 --> 00:11:38,350
Then it's our second movie,

276
00:11:38,350 --> 00:11:39,470
followed by our third movie.

277
00:11:39,470 --> 00:11:40,630
